Hi! 👋 
      
Firstly, thanks for your work on this project! 🙂

Today I used [patch-package](https://github.com/ds300/patch-package) to patch `exceljs@4.4.0` for the project I'm working on.

<!-- 🔺️🔺️🔺️ PLEASE REPLACE THIS BLOCK with a description of your problem, and any other relevant context 🔺️🔺️🔺️ -->

Here is the diff that solved my problem:

```diff
diff --git a/node_modules/exceljs/index.d.ts b/node_modules/exceljs/index.d.ts
index 5979806..3e4da34 100644
--- a/node_modules/exceljs/index.d.ts
+++ b/node_modules/exceljs/index.d.ts
@@ -1078,6 +1078,8 @@ export interface DataBarRuleType extends ConditionalFormattingBaseRule {
 	axisPosition?: 'auto' | 'middle' | 'none';
 	direction?: 'context' | 'leftToRight' | 'rightToLeft';
 	cfvo?: Cvfo[];
+  color?: Partial<Color>;
+  negativeFillColor?: Partial<Color>;
 }
 
 export type ConditionalFormattingRule = ExpressionRuleType | CellIsRuleType | Top10RuleType | AboveAverageRuleType | ColorScaleRuleType | IconSetRuleType
diff --git a/node_modules/exceljs/lib/xlsx/xform/sheet/worksheet-xform.js b/node_modules/exceljs/lib/xlsx/xform/sheet/worksheet-xform.js
index b389300..b20bd08 100644
--- a/node_modules/exceljs/lib/xlsx/xform/sheet/worksheet-xform.js
+++ b/node_modules/exceljs/lib/xlsx/xform/sheet/worksheet-xform.js
@@ -353,6 +353,8 @@ class WorkSheetXform extends BaseXform {
       });
     }
 
+    // Ignore error number store as text
+    xmlStream._xml.push("<ignoredErrors><ignoredError sqref=\"A1:XFD1048576\" numberStoredAsText=\"1\" /></ignoredErrors>");
     xmlStream.closeNode();
   }
 
```

